{
  "stem": "3012.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It, it turned out that there was a synthetic rubber factory in Monowitz a couple of kilometers from Auschwitz where they had Auschwitz prisoners working there as slave laborers.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Totally disoriented, totally.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I mean, the, the normal perception of reality just cut off from one second to the other.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] They took us to lager B3.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was a number of meters-- I mean, a good number of meters from the man's camp, and behind the man's camp-- I'm talking about Birkenau, not Auschwitz-- from the gypsy camp.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "As it turned out, we stayed in block 10, and then in block five.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There was an extremely vicious blockalteste by the name of Mala, M-A-L-A.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The blockalteste was the woman-- the Jewish woman supervisor who was running that particular block where they put us up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a series of small huts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They jammed in at least 1,000 or 1,200-- I don't know how many women.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In block 10, or five, or anywhere in lager B3, there were no cots.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They made us lie on the floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had my head on the rear end of the inmate before me, and on my rear end was resting the prisoner whose turn it was to be there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So, if during the night somebody had to go to the latrine, couldn't find a place to sit down, less to sleep.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was with my mother in my aunt, and somehow-- I don't know what made us think-- from then on, I never ever called her mother.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I only called her Sari.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They did not know, except the people from our town, that we are relatives because it was not good to have a relative in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know who told us.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
